"violet-300 underline-offset-2 hover:text-violet-700 dark:text-"
"violet-400\">EAS</a>, reputation can become portable, transparent, and hard "
"to fake — proofs you carry into other apps and agent ecosystems."
msgstr ""
"Con <a href=\"https://attest.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener "
"noreferrer\" class=\"font-medium text-violet-600 underline decoration-"
"violet-300 underline-offset-2 hover:text-violet-700 dark:text-"
"violet-400\">EAS</a>, la reputación puede volverse portátil, transparente y "
